      "title": "Limited Bus Services on Monday (29)",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Lanka Private Bus Owners' Association says that a significant number of buses will operate today (29).",
        "The limited number of services is mainly due to the Diesel shortage experienced in many parts of the country.",
        "The Chairman of Lanka Private Bus Owners' Association Gemunu Wijeratne said that if fuel is received properly, all buses will operate in the coming days.",
        "Over 1,000 people killed by Pakistan monsoon rains and floods"
